{"tid":2265423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰黃衫軍倡政變 副總理拒絕","createTime":"2020-10-31T12:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T13:26:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff4be2a43b088cecf677b17adbd5ff87afa0bf0","tid":2265423,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201031/2P6SH67JYJGYNPBYASWX674QGY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201031%2F2P6SH67JYJGYNPBYASWX674QGY%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0UsakzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=3af4ea2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201031%2F2P6SH67JYJGYNPBYASWX674QGY%2F&h=a811a056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201031/2P6SH67JYJGYNPBYASWX674QGY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n泰黃衫軍倡政變 副總理拒絕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QM6vdKUdTCeLjfGjGU5kica3m4k=/1575x1031/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7LFAMNHTX5GCJIF4XBN3X7TVTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQM6vdKUdTCeLjfGjGU5kica3m4k%3D%2F1575x1031%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7LFAMNHTX5GCJIF4XBN3X7TVTM.jpg&h=c6b2f7cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■示威者前晚在曼谷街道鋪紅地毯模擬時裝表演，跟同日泰王設計師女兒的時裝展打對台。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n泰國反對派要求政制和王室改革的立場未有退讓迹象，有親王室社運人士近日主張再發動政變組成大聯盟政府，但副總理巴威前日已明言拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n前黃衫軍領袖林明達周二接受表示政變不是禍害，認為如需要修訂憲法，所有參與者要有權發言和確保章程公平，也要成立獨立的大。。。。。。。。。。對此，巴威前日只簡單地回應：「不會有任何政變。」<br />\n<br />\n反對派近日最高調的行動為遊行到曼谷的德國大使館，要求德方調查泰王哇集拉隆功旅居德國時有否違法地管理泰國事務。。。。。。。。。。。。，預料撤銷泰王國家元首身份的簽證會引發外交風波。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泰王主持畢業禮 學生抵制<br />\n<br />\n在近日示威中擔當重要角色的法政大學昨日和今日舉行畢業典禮，儀式如以往一樣由泰王主持，遭部份學生抵制，如23歲的素班那希望盡量減少出席人數，表達有人不滿君主制和希望改變。但24歲的巴邦功表示會參與，要在這一生人一次的機會拍照留念。亦有人坦言不想出席，只是家長要求他到場。<br />\n<br />\n泰國《曼谷郵報》/路透社"},{"pid":"2cc53d559f2cefdef0a33860051d9a7f1f5d4a11","tid":2265423,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:20:39.000Z","msg":"即係中國共產黨推翻中國共產黨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882b1459217d5d0ef443c88c00dd254a431d9903","tid":2265423,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:22:08.000Z","msg":"泰國手足好有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f6629ea61f25b506e336c6369564c67bdf2b17","tid":2265423,"uid":245849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2cc53d559f2cefdef0a33860051d9a7f1f5d4a11","tid":2265423,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:20:39.000Z","msg":"即係中國共產黨推翻中國共產黨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:48:20.000Z","msg":"泰國情況唔同<br />\n<br />\n你當民建聯建議林鄭落台換人"},{"pid":"090c7325424659adb9e4fb3ca8ff2d1ff82fe3e4","tid":2265423,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cc53d559f2cefdef0a33860051d9a7f1f5d4a11","tid":2265423,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:20:39.000Z","msg":"即係中國共產黨推翻中國共產黨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:49:23.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">係習近平落台，換個減速師上台咁解</span>"},{"pid":"5bdee98f081b6258c374e4e7b9a5e33f21827692","tid":2265423,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cc53d559f2cefdef0a33860051d9a7f1f5d4a11","tid":2265423,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:20:39.000Z","msg":"即係中國共產黨推翻中國共產黨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:49:23.000Z","msg":"支持江派人馬復辟 取代習近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"